"海岸地域生態調査":
"At the coastal area of planet Vopar,
native creatures known as Oceanids
have been spotted.

They've been influenced by Darkers and
are especially agressive towards Arks.
Arks personnel are to deal with the
threat and investigate.
――――――――――――――――――――
Clear: Collect [200] Quest Points
by defeating Oceanids."
